description: TC Tech Sweden AB engages in the development of advanced plastic. The company is headquartered in Spanga, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2015-11-30. The firm focuses on the manufacture of Light Guide Plates (LGP) used in the production of screens and displays to direct and scatter light out the front. The firm supplies systems for the screen industry. The Company’s products include TCP 1000 High Performance (HP), TCP 1000 High Throughput (HT), TCP 150 High Precision Electric (HPE) and TCP Edge Embossing (EE). The firm has its statutory seat and head office in Karlshamn, Sweden, whereas Research and Development (R&D) operations are based in Stockholm (Spanga), Sweden.
